Class CollegeChecking

java.lang.Object
com.example.rubank.Account
com.example.rubank.Checking
com.example.rubank.CollegeChecking
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Account>
public class CollegeChecking extends Checking
CollegeChecking class inherits from Checking class and represents a college checking account with a profile, balance, and campus.
Author:
Pranay Bhatt and Fiona Wang
